cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.SY 

The paper deals with the application of neural networks to solve optimization problems subject to constraints. This falls under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). The paper also proposes a new method for imposing equality constraints, which is relevant to the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the advantages of the proposed method in terms of locality, which is relevant to the field of systems and control (cs.SY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
